Feature: Currency changing

  Scenario: View prices in dollar
    Given user is on layout8 page
    Then user wants to view prices in dollar
    When user hovers over currency icon
    And selects dollar from the dropdown
    Then see prices in dollar

  Scenario: View prices in pounds
    Given user is on layout8 page
    Then user wants to view prices in pounds
    When user hovers over currency icon
    And selects pounds from the dropdown
    Then see prices in pounds

  Scenario: View prices in euro
    Given user is on layout8 page
    Then user wants to view prices in euro
    When user hovers over currency icon
    And selects pounds from the dropdown
    Then see prices in euro
